mvector LOCAL mvector

NAME

mjo_vector_pop — remove the last element from a vector

SYNOPSIS

#include <mvector.h>

void
mjo_vector_pop(mjo_vector_t const io_var);

DESCRIPTION

Remove the last element from a vector. Following, the discharge method, if any, will be invoked on that object.

Following is a description of the arguments.

io_var
pointer to a ‘mjo_vector_t’ to pop an element from

If io_var is nil or the number of elements in the vector is zero, no operations will be peformed.

The number of elements in the vector will decrease by one.
